### ==================== USER ENDPOINTS ====================

### Register User
POST {{baseUrl}}/users/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "user_{{$timestamp}}@example.com",
  "phone": "030012345{{$randomInt(10,99)}}",
  "password": "Test@123456",
  "firstName": "John",
  "lastName": "Doe"
}

### Login User
POST {{baseUrl}}/users/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "testuser@example.com",
  "password": "Test@123456"
}

### Get Current User Profile (Protected)
GET {{baseUrl}}/users/profile
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Get User by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/users/{{userId}}

### Update User Profile (Protected)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/users/profile
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

{
  "firstName": "Jane",
  "lastName": "Smith",
  "phone": "030098765{{$randomInt(10,99)}}"
}

### Change Password (Protected)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/users/change-password
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

{
  "currentPassword": "Test@123456",
  "newPassword": "NewPassword@123"
}

### Delete User Account (Protected)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/users/account
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### ==================== ISSUE ENDPOINTS ====================

### Create Issue (Protected)
POST {{baseUrl}}/issues
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

{
  "title": "Broken Water Pipe",
  "description": "Water pipe is broken near the market. Wasting a lot of water.",
  "category": "Water",
  "latitude": 34.0522,
  "longitude": -118.2437,
  "address": "Downtown Los Angeles",
  "image": "https://example.com/water-pipe-issue.jpg"
}

### Get All Issues
GET {{baseUrl}}/issues

### Get All Issues - Filter by Category
GET {{baseUrl}}/issues?category=Water

### Get All Issues - Filter by Status
GET {{baseUrl}}/issues?status=Pending

### Get All Issues - Filter by User
GET {{baseUrl}}/issues?userId={{userId}}

### Get Issue by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/issues/{{issueId}}

### Get Nearby Issues
GET {{baseUrl}}/issues/nearby?latitude=34.0522&longitude=-118.2437&radius=5

### Update Issue (Protected)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/issues/{{issueId}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

{
  "title": "Updated Issue Title",
  "description": "Updated description",
  "status": "In Progress",
  "category": "Electricity"
}

### Delete Issue (Protected)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/issues/{{issueId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### ==================== UPVOTE ENDPOINTS ====================

### Add Upvote (Protected)
POST {{baseUrl}}/upvotes
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

{
  "issueId": "{{issueId}}"
}

### Get Upvotes for Issue
GET {{baseUrl}}/upvotes/issue/{{issueId}}

### Check if User Upvoted (Protected)
GET {{baseUrl}}/upvotes/check/{{issueId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Get User's Upvoted Issues (Protected)
GET {{baseUrl}}/upvotes/user/my-upvotes
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Remove Upvote (Protected)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/upvotes/{{issueId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### ==================== COMMENT ENDPOINTS ====================

### Create Comment (Protected)
POST {{baseUrl}}/comments
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

{
  "issueId": "{{issueId}}",
  "text": "This issue needs urgent attention! The infrastructure is collapsing."
}

### Get Comments for Issue
GET {{baseUrl}}/comments/issue/{{issueId}}

### Get Single Comment
GET {{baseUrl}}/comments/{{commentId}}

### Update Comment (Protected)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/comments/{{commentId}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

{
  "text": "Updated comment text"
}

### Delete Comment (Protected)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/comments/{{commentId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Get Comments by User
GET {{baseUrl}}/comments/user/{{userId}}

### ==================== HEALTH CHECK ====================

### Server Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health
